text: If you are a participant of #UKBiobank you can visit the participant website: https://t.co/S0meAMXEQS and select the 'coronavirus research' button to volunteer.

urls.title: UKB : Login to Participant Section
urls.description: You are a Participant in UK Biobank if you gave consent at an Assessment Centre and have not withdrawn from the study. To begin, enter your details below and click Login. For more information, press the help icons. If you have forgotten your Participant ID then please click HERE. If you are unable to use this website then please telephone our Participant Resource Centre on 0800 0 276 276 for assistance. WARNING: your browser does NOT have JavaScript enabled. You may not be able to submit data. Please
